<div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2"><div class="modal-body">
<h2>Vega Media Group</h2>
<p class="item-intro"></p> <img decoding="async" class="img-responsive img-centered" src="./wp-content/blogs.dir/10/files/sites/15/2017/12/vega-logo-02a.png" alt="Vega Media Group"><p>Vega Media Group is a media company that serves a variety of businesses. We provide strategic advertising, digital, print, search, social and content marketing – locally, regionally and nationally.  Our influence is unmatched in the region.  As Rose City’s leading news source and publisher of The Rose Cityian / Rose City Live, we have years of experience and deep connections in the community. We bring powerful digital marketing solutions and local insights to the businesses we work with.</p> <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i> Close Project</button>
