<div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2"><div class="modal-body">
<h2>Sunrise Protection</h2>
<p class="item-intro">Over a Decade of Unrivaled Protection Services</p> <img decoding="async" class="img-responsive img-centered" src="./wp-content/blogs.dir/10/files/sites/15/2017/12/Sunrise-1.png" alt="Sunrise Protection"><p>Sunrise Protection started in response to professional private security demand in the business community. We ease the burden of law enforcement for minor issues; although at no point and time do we act as a law enforcement agent through our performance of duties. Sunrise Protection streamlines and magnifies our customer service goals in order to ensure that each customer’s unique needs are met and quality service is delivered.  Sunrise Protection employees – partners in our success – vigorously uphold our mission statement in every assignment. Our customers have responded tremendously and their support of our commitment has enabled Sunrise Protection the ability to offer a variety of in-house and out-of-house training for our employees. This, in turn, allows Sunrise Protection to offer a higher quality of professional service to our customers.  With the entire staff of Sunrise Protection sharing our vision of distinctive quality and unparalleled customer service, we are headed for greater success in the future.</p> <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i> Close Project</button>
</div></div></div></div>
